./my-claw/sdp/prd-agent-runtime-substrate.md:13:This PRD creates a shared runtime substrate for all agent execution. The goal is one execution layer with durable session semantics, consistent streaming, clear interrupts, and observable process health.
./my-claw/sdp/prd-agent-runtime-substrate.md:15:This is not a UI PRD. It is the execution machinery that makes the rest of the organism feel continuous rather than stateless.
