./sdp/logs/Lead_T-001_20260408T223256Z_1775688053.log:575:./sdp/logs/Lead_T-001_20260408T223256Z_1775687592.log:1611:my-claw/sdp/prd-r750-ollama-integration.md:5:The Dell PowerEdge R750 (2x Xeon Silver 4310, 813GB RAM, no GPU) will run PromptClaw with Ollama as a first-class local agent alongside claude/codex/gemini. This PRD covers the code changes needed to integrate Ollama into the existing daemon architecture. No architectural rewrites — extend what exists.
