./my-claw/sdp/prd-context-engine.md:1:# PRD: Context Engine — Compaction, Session Briefs, and Operational Memory
./my-claw/sdp/prd-context-engine.md:5:CypherClaw currently carries context through a shallow rolling conversation buffer, scattered status helpers, and whatever the active agent can infer from the workspace. That is not enough for a long-running artistic system that must remember what changed, what failed, what is in progress, and what still matters after a restart or a handoff.
./my-claw/sdp/prd-context-engine.md:7:This PRD creates an operational context engine.
